A Legacy of Excellence
Founded over six decades ago, the University of Novi Sad Serbia  has a rich and storied history. From its humble beginnings as a small faculty of agriculture, it has expanded to encompass a wide range of disciplines and faculties, earning a reputation for academic excellence and innovation. Today, the university continues to build upon its legacy, striving to provide students with a world-class education that prepares them for success in an ever-changing world.

